Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: Jesse Watters: “Three years ago, Kamala Harris looked you in the eye and lied about border patrol ‘whipping’ Haitian migrants. Fast-forward three years, and more than three-hundred-thousand Haitians are living here legally thanks to Harris-Biden. How has it been going? Look no further than Springfield, Ohio — the epicenter of the migrant crisis in middle America…”
